        <item>
            <title>【实试】Fujifilm Instax mini 99 玩光影效果，有玩味的即影即有相机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-mini-99</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax mini 99]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[即影即有相机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232168</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不少人用手机影相，po 上 IG 都会加滤镜。今次这部全新即影即有相机 Fujifilm Instax mini 99 都可以玩类似效果，制造到不同滤镜效果之余，竟不用数码执相，更加原始、更 RAW 更有味道！以下小编就会同 unwire 记者沙律同大家一齐实试。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232198" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>色彩效果＝物理灯光效果超好玩</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax mini 99 是 mini 90 的升级版本，但就带来了两个极之好玩的升级新功能。包括有类似滤镜的「色彩效果控制」功能，还有模仿怀旧相机的晕影功能。虽然设计简单，但试过之后实在好玩到停唔到手！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>首先介绍「色彩效果控制」功能。简单来说就是类似手机 App 的相片滤镜，但这部相机就完全没有「数码味」。打开相机盖，你可看到镜头后方有 4 颗会发光、变色的 LED 灯，在拍摄时发出不同颜色的光芒，直接将色相打入菲林中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>你可透过相机侧边的转盘，设定预设定义的颜色组合，包括有 Normal、Fraded Green、Warm Tone、Light Blue、Soft Magenta、Sepia，以及 Light Leak。虽然此功能纯粹简单打灯入菲林，但出来的效果却令人有惊喜。每张相片都各有风格，适合不同场合使用。即使你跟朋友在同一场地拍照，都可影出不同效果，增添了相片的变化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左手边的转盘可调节不同的光影效果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Normal</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Fraded Green</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Warm Tone</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Light Blue</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Soft Magenta</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sepia</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Light Leak</p><h2>物理「晕影」令相片更有 feel</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax mini 99 更加入「晕影模式」，可物理模拟古典相机镜头的晕影（黑角）效果。「晕影模式」同样不是数码化植入相片，而是靠相机镜头前的「VIGNETTE」拨杆。将此拨杆拨向有效时，相机镜头面前就会加入一道物理屏障，令你拍出来的相片直接产生黑角。虽然设计简单，但拍摄出来的效果也是同样有惊喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲未开晕影模式，请留意镜头中间的镜片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在开启晕影模式后，可看到镜头玻璃被一层叶片物理覆盖，制造成人为的「晕影」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除了上面两个新玩法，Instax mini 99 备有 5 个等级的光度调节。好多人认为 Instax 的相片不够光，现在你就可自由调校曝光度。从 D-, D, -, L, L+ 共 5 级光度水平。简单来说相片愈光就愈低反差、低对比，让你在日光拍摄时增添日系风味。而较黑的相片则会看上去较高对比，有另一番风味。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Instax mini 99 与上代 mini 90 一样设有风景、微距模式。在相机镜头的转盘上，你可调校 0.3~0.6m、0.6m~3m，以及 3m~ 无限远，适合不同拍摄情景。在拍摄小物时，利用 0.3~0.6m 模式，就可做到了一点浅景深效果。另外相机自拍功能、双重曝光模式都在 mini 99 上用到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次 mini 99 采用可拆卸式电池，并随产品附有充电机，让你随时充电。产品更有一个可插在三脚架螺纹的手柄，让你在自拍时更加轻松。</p><p>Instax mini 99 发售日期：2024 年 4 月 25 日</p><p>建议零售价：HK$1,580</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/fujifilm-gfx100s-xt50-mirrorless-camera-may-16/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">网络爆料 Fujifilm GFX100S II   联同 X-T50 无反相机 5 月中发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/29/fujifilm-limited-edition-camera/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">庆祝品牌成立 90 周年，限量版 Fujifilm X100VI 中国消费者有额外著数</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Fujifilm X100VI 外观流出　新机疑剔除 D-Pad</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/">【实试】Fujifilm Instax mini 99 玩光影效果，有玩味的即影即有相机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
